{"tid":159320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"避孕套藏港幣塞私處 4女拱北走私27萬被截","createTime":"2017-03-17T01:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T09:46:44.000Z","uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc6706c339981b0710b40af4d69daa3b1fb5551","tid":159320,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170316&amp;guid=56438528&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170316%26guid%3D56438528%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=09261594\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170316%26guid%3D56438528%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=e058f55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170316&amp;guid=56438528&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n珠海拱北海關近日破獲4宗水客利用人體藏匿走私港幣出境案件。其中兩名涉案女水客，將走私過關的港幣藏在避孕套內，然後再塞進私處，再穿貼身衣物遮掩，是近13年來首次截獲的私處走私港幣案。海關指，4宗案件所涉及的港幣合共27.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n拱北海關表示，本月9日上午10至11時，拱北口岸緝私民警根據情報，於出境大廳旅檢無申報通道先後截查多名水客，包括3名分別姓梁、譚及馮的內地中年婦人，以及一名姓魏的澳門婦女，詢問有否攜帶需申報物品。當時，4人均答沒有。<br />\n<br />\n女關員先後將4人帶至封閉區搜身，從梁X的內褲和私處內分別取出5萬和7.5萬港元、從覃X私處內取出7.5萬港元。兩名女子均將港元捲成圓筒再用避孕套裹緊後塞入隱私部位。女關員亦從馮X的貼身衣物內查出2.5萬港元，等候檢查的澳門婦女魏X見狀，自行從貼身衣物內取出5萬港元。4人目前正由海關緝私部門進一步處理。其中，梁X、覃X利用私處走私港元出境，是拱北海關近13年來查獲的首起利用人體藏匿走私外幣案。<br />\n<br />\n拱北關員表示，內地對外匯管制自去年底起趨嚴，外幣走私案隨之趨增。橫琴海關於上月17至18日的短短廿四小時內，連續查獲13宗外幣走私案，截獲的外幣折合約321萬人民幣。今年1月14日拱北關員截查澳門女子周X時，查獲其隨身藏有222萬澳門元。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8fci66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8fci66.jpg&h=f3837063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1db03a3f33c3d2c62452fb0a01af0ba10b54152d","tid":159320,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"睇撚錯硬幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf84c6254b2afd5a12817779205e17c467941e7","tid":159320,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇撚錯硬幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b2453e719675c6e922896e131af3ca7d2a941c","tid":159320,"uid":2655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b752634f341a2d7034337c2da5531f7119c9fc4","tid":159320,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb9423b6d25f07059b7d77e0427a2d7d565529","tid":159320,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌"},{"pid":"e26aa0ce0d6abd8391b36e5b873cfbc5775b7a95","tid":159320,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"啲銀紙唔該匯豐盡快回收<br />\n之後搵生化回收公司燒毁咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cbfdc830cb85d7fd85445a5fff2a1ecde32289","tid":159320,"uid":9740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"西隧"},{"pid":"7f7d3ca476793ebf15f31738e0d544edb0d0a78c","tid":159320,"uid":73057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌</blockquote><br />\n窒左嘢, 屌唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad679cdee2107570ce8c635224a9f203c13eceaa","tid":159320,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:43:20.000